{
  "stem": "2350.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So all Germans on the first [INAUDIBLE], the first patrol took already-- they were already in my hometown.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were already, 10 kilometers later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we stood them-- they were white-faced, because the roads were full of dust.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you could see just the glasses that they had and the red lips.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't do anything to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We stood there, and we says, the Germans are here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What's next?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we stayed another day with my uncle, wherever there was room to sleep.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, the next day, we started going back home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I says, if the Germans are here and they were in my house, so what's the use staying here?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we rode back home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the German marched and they marched, by the thousands.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were going home with the horse and wagon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By the thousands, they were going and taking over Poland, piece by piece, piece by piece.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't do, then, anything to us yet, because this was the first troops.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we arrived back home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then you started to put your life back together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So there is, right away, no school, no walking out after 8:00.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They started taking over the businesses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Germans made like a Jewish Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is a Jewish committee to manage the Jews, to know who was what and where.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was a beautiful park in Zawiercie, one of the nicest in Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was right away a sign for Jews, no entry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN], this means Jews cannot go there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So life started to go down the drain.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The food was scarce.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They started giving us cards for food rations.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And you went to the store, and there was no food.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
